[center][size=3][b]Base Commander Level Costs[/b][/size] (In Progress)[/center]
Consider Construction commanders for each base and a research commander for each base you conduct research. The cost of a level 10 construction commander is 4,536 credits. Building planetary rings alone would pay for the commander in savings, not to mention the fact that the commander also reduces the construction time.
